，佢地咪引返自己啲文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"咁歐美學術界都係咁玩"},{"pid":"2f2f6cd1de4596bf9d0f7b0a591c7f1e13512383","tid":1062091,"uid":64051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe2bb47784a2e82173fa7a01cd5ac7b26dd02353","tid":1062091,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115e064b09132e6f85eac9492b44d7c69be16bd5","tid":1062091,"uid":232817,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"依啲引文數冇意義，佢地最鍾意cite返自己啲野灌水，有啲statement係普通事實，佢地咪引返自己啲文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"不過而家學術界大趨勢都係睇引用IF"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"IF？非學術人，可唔可以解釋下<br />\n因為之前又係有個大陸打丁報告話啲論文點點點，想知真實情況"},{"pid":"8ec88a2d6712ddac16402a37f77efe7febf4f578","tid":1062091,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"升排名, 打飛機岩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1371f02bad6cbe93c6237f827a35a865e25acf2","tid":1062091,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f2f6cd1de4596bf9d0f7b0a591c7f1e13512383","tid":1062091,"uid":64051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe2bb47784a2e82173fa7a01cd5ac7b26dd02353","tid":1062091,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115e064b09132e6f85eac9492b44d7c69be16bd5","tid":1062091,"uid":232817,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"依啲引文數冇意義，佢地最鍾意cite返自己啲野灌水，有啲statement係普通事實，佢地咪引返自己啲文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"不過而家學術界大趨勢都係睇引用IF"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"IF？非學術人，可唔可以解釋下<br />\n因為之前又係有個大陸打丁報告話啲論文點點點，想知真實情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"IF = impact factor<br />\n簡單黎講就係係結算年份(e.g. 2018)前 N 年 (official 係3年, 但亦都有5年IF, 計5年, 即係official睇 2015-2017) 的publication 係 2018年平均有幾多個citations<br />\n而impact factor一般用黎比較期刊, 但係唔同subfield可以差好遠, 例如medicine閒閒地有20 - 30, 但係人文數學